# Ad-hoc microbench artifacts under tests/.  The cmake/qmake test suite
# uses fixed names (alloc_stress_test, transaction_*) and stays tracked;
# anything matching `tests/bench_*` is an experiment binary or source
# file used to tune the allocator against mimalloc / sys malloc and
# gets regenerated per run.  Excluded so paper-data collection doesn't
# pollute `git status`.
tests/bench_*
tests/bench_*.dSYM/

# cmake/ctest output (CTest writes "Testing/Temporary/" with last-run
# logs).  Build-dir-local; never tracked.
Testing/
